data.description: Los Fresnos, TX. Spacious 4BR+1office 3 baths home available in a well established & family friendly area in the up & coming neighborhood. This lovely abode is ready for picturesque memories to be made from family get togethers on the well manicured lawn to holiday hugs&grand welcomes in the beautiful foyer. This home is perfect for that entrepreneurial power couple who need an extra guest suite for those helpful in-law, live-in nanny or just an extra fully equipped guest chamber to treat your company like royalty. The primary suite really is fit for a well groomed king & queen with its storage filled "his & hers" vanity stations. Must see this space in person with its vaulted ceilings and spacious commons areas. Kitchen features custom cabinets with beautiful natural granite countertops+. Recent renovations include: fresh paint, shingles replaced 11/22, water heater 07/23,5 Ton AC 06/22 all appliances included, ready storage shed. Call today!
